Pre-Game Insights: Harambee Stars coach was bullish after the last round of fixtures saying ‘am not afraid of Cameroon’
Miscellaneous Highlights: This is the second time the two sides have met at this stage (AFCON qualifiers)
Others: Kenya has never beaten Cameroon in 8 different encounters. They have drawn 4 times and have lost the rest while scoring 7 goals. Cameroon on their part have found the net 14 times against Kenya.
